Gharull is the charismatic head of the [[Ashbound]] [[druid]] sect. A fiery and passionate [[shifter]], Gharull firmly believes he speaks with nature's voice. No small number of druids have joined the sect primarily because of Gharull's magnetic presence; he has an uncanny ability to convince anyone who hears him speak of the righteousness of his cause.